<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/389066-the-bridge-to-total-freedom-through">&quot;the Bridge to Total Freedom, through which members gain eternal life.&quot;

Wouldn&#39;t it be far more correct to have said, &quot;the Bridge to Total Freedom, through which members are said to gain eternal life.&quot;??</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_389066'><a id="like_count_community_question_389066" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/389066?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F16142053-going-clear">like</a></span>

